Luis Andres Cuyun, 30, was gunned down by two suspected Mara Salvatrucha gang members in Guatemala City on Friday morning .
The director of a jail for young gang members was killed in the attack .
A Salvadoran man arrested for alleged involvement in the shooting was also arrested .
Juan Carlos Medina Luna, 29, and Mario Alfonso Aguilar, 18, were arrested after a short police chase .